fulltitle: Making 'Rush To Judgement': Mark Lane and Robert Primes recorded by Randy Benson (2013)
title: Making 'Rush To Judgement': Mark Lane and Robert Primes recorded by Randy Benson (2013)
_filename: _Making 'Rush To Judgement' - Mark Lane and Robert Primes recorded by Randy Benson (2013).webm
description:
Prior to the screening of the 1966 film, Rush To Judgment (cdsporch.org/archives/20303), Writer/Producer Mark Lane and Cinematographer Robert Primes, appeared via online stream for a brief discussion.

Recorded by Randolph Benson, Oct 28 2013
